{"tid":1916331,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"現任同前度，你會點揀？(唔比鬧人臭雞）有無一個你放唔低既佢？","createTime":"2020-03-08T19:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T00:54:11.000Z","uid":322094,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5b657132336132e62b557bfe53015052499993","tid":1916331,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T19:59:37.000Z","msg":"對唔住，fake左你入黎，不過我真係想搵人聽我呷下<br />\n<br />\n話說f5-6個時，我同我初戀拍左年半<br />\n佢好到傻（唔詳列住）<br />\n我地見哂對方朋友&amp;家長，熱戀期好似無停過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都覺得我地係golden couple<br />\n有時我地會ff下將來，佢話過唔會走<br />\n但最後因為某d原因 我地都係分開左（以前真係太幼稚）<br />\n<br />\n一年過後，佢變左好多，唔再係我鍾意既佢....但<br />\n我個腦不時都仲會loop起以前好好既回憶 有時仲諗到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（even我依加有男朋友）<br />\n<br />\n失戀真係好痛好痛，唔知要用幾耐先可以痊愈<br />\n我好中意依加男朋友，所以我喊既其中一個原因係因為好怕再失去，好怕再無左一個好重要既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好怕佢會唔要我<br />\n<br />\n今晚喊左一陣之後，好想打電話同佢講我好愛佢，好想攬住佢，好想佢同我講話「唔會再hurt我 唔會掉低我」<br />\n（好啦其實我最後有打電話俾佢 不過佢冇聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我男朋友份人好踏實，唔會亂咁promise d佢未必做到既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以平時我地一提到長遠少少既事，佢都會避而不談，<br />\n更加唔好講話會ff將來，佢極其量都係會話「我唔會走...住」唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但女人真係好鍾意聽大話，尤其是我唔開心嗰陣時更加想佢會同我講佢會一直都係到，但佢就死都唔肯講，跟住自己個心就un住un住咁，我都覺得自己好傻鳩唔知點算，但我又唔敢同我男朋友講，怕佢亂諗唔開心"},{"pid":"2cac78715c9aba1bfac6cbcacf1773dbc3c36eae","tid":1916331,"uid":15605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:15:47.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"ae7be65532bad354451e2b9ffa5560b2e225bd40","tid":1916331,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cac78715c9aba1bfac6cbcacf1773dbc3c36eae","tid":1916331,"uid":15605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:15:47.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:17:58.000Z","msg":"燥底痴線佬"},{"pid":"c4a96f616149922e58402f82a0919cd969dc29f6","tid":1916331,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae7be65532bad354451e2b9ffa5560b2e225bd40","tid":1916331,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cac78715c9aba1bfac6cbcacf1773dbc3c36eae","tid":1916331,"uid":15605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:15:47.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:17:58.000Z","msg":"燥底痴線佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:18:17.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"f3796abdf62c6169f8c736d80300e2ad4ca12293","tid":1916331,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4a96f616149922e58402f82a0919cd969dc29f6","tid":1916331,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae7be65532bad354451e2b9ffa5560b2e225bd40","tid":1916331,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cac78715c9aba1bfac6cbcacf1773dbc3c36eae","tid":1916331,"uid":15605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:15:47.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:17:58.000Z","msg":"燥底痴線佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:18:17.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T20:19:03.000Z","msg":"燥底痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4673ab993433e8da1b1b799b30fa03466350e9","tid":1916331,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3796abdf62c6169f8c736d80300e2ad4ca12293","tid":1916331,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4a96f616149922e58402f82a0919cd969dc29f6","tid":1916331,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae7be65532bad354451e2b9ffa5560b2e225bd40","tid":1916331,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl